<topic class="Popup" template="Default" status="Under Construction" modified="2022-07-22T10:33:35.569+01:00" lasteditedby="Adam" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>Ball-Joints</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Ball-Joint<keyword>Definition</keyword><keyword>Spherical-Joint</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>Definition<keyword>Ball-Joint</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="2" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:120px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-BallJoints-ConnectingPart-Pop.ipp" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joints</text> - add as sets of two(2) with one(1) <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text> at each end of one(1) <text styleclass="Element">Part</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-1.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text> two <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Points</text> from two <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">parts</text> in <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Mechanism B</text><text styleclass="Image Caption">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint -</text> one <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Point</text> in <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Mechanism B,</text> one <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Point</text> in <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Mechanism &#160;A</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2">Connecting Part</text><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">&#32;</text>: the<text styleclass="Popup Box2">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> to which you add a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joints</text><image src="Red-14-1.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> at each end.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2" style="width:281px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Other names for a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text> in the engineering community are: <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Rod-End</text>&#32;<text styleclass="VariableName-small">Bearing</text>, <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Heim Joint (USA), Rose-Joint Bearing (UK).</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See more: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Connecting-Part">Connecting-Part</link></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddBall-Joint">Add Ball-Joint</link>, &#160;<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-BallJoint">Ball-Joint dialog-box</link>; <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Ball-Joint-Configurations">Ball-Joint Configurations</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
